  "body": "Shouldn't the parent constructor be called?\r\n\r\ncurrently:\r\n`  function CappedCrowdsale(uint256 _cap) {\r\n    require(_cap > 0);\r\n    cap = _cap;\r\n  }`\r\n\r\nproposed:\r\n`  function CappedCrowdsale(uint256 _cap, uint256 _startTime, uint256 _endTime, uint256 _rate, address _wallet) Crowdsale(_startTime, _endTime, _rate, _wallet) {\r\n    require(_cap > 0);\r\n    cap = _cap;\r\n  }`",
